### Electronics Shop API Tests
### Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code to use this file

### Variables
@host = http://localhost:5000
@api = /api/products

### 1. Get All Products
GET {{host}}{{api}}

### 2. Get Single Product (replace with actual ID)
GET {{host}}{{api}}/PRODUCT_ID_HERE

