### 13. Update Product (replace PRODUCT_ID)
PUT {{host}}{{api}}/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 100000,
  "inStock": false
}

### 14. Delete Product (replace PRODUCT_ID)
DELETE {{host}}{{api}}/PRODUCT_ID_HERE

### Notes:
### - After creating a product, copy the _id from response to use in GET/PUT/DELETE requests
### - All prices are in KES (Kenyan Shillings)
### - Categories: Phones, Laptops, Audio, Wearables, Tablets
### - Images use placeholder service (you can replace with real image URLs)
